  "description": "OUROBOROS's strange attractor waveforms become the FM modulator for ORGANON's metabolic synthesis — chaos feeds the organism. Each note receives the attractor's phase position at that moment as its FM input, so no two voices ever have identical modulation. ORGANON's Variational Free Energy metabolism ingests the chaos per-voice. The result: polyphony with inherent timbral variance, never repeating.",
